Clefairy

Evolves At 4

Magic Guard

Passive Ability

This Pokémon receives a shield when restoring an ally Pokémon's HP. The strength of this shield is proportional to 50% of the amount of HP restored.

Attack

Auto Attack

Becomes a boosted attack with every third attack, dealing increased damage.

100% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

69% SpA + 17 x (Level - 1) + 320

Heal Pulse

Move 1

7.00s Recovery

Immediately restores HP to itself and nearby allies.

90% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 300

Heal Pulse Upgrade Choices

Moonlight

8.00s Recovery

Continually restores HP to Clefable and nearby allies for 3s at one tick per half second excluding activation at 0s. Clefable’s movement speed is increased by 20% while this move is active.

61.6% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 55

Widens this move’s area-of-effect and increases the duration of its effects by 1s.

Draining Kiss

4.00s Recovery

Attacks nearby enemies with an energy-draining kiss. Each enemy hit by the kiss receives damage and releases an air kiss. These air kisses will travel to a nearby ally with the lowest HP and restore their HP. If no allies are near, the air kisses will return to Clefable and restore its HP for 100% of the damage dealt.

159% SpA + 26 x (Level - 1) + 580

Widens this move’s area-of-effect and increases the amount of HP restored to 120% of the damage dealt.

Disarming Voice

Move 2

9.00s Area

Let out a charming cry, dealing damage to nearby enemies and decreasing their movement speed by 40% for 2s.

113% SpA + 19 x (Level - 1) + 590

Disarming Voice Upgrade Choices

Gravity

8.00s Hindrance

Create a gravity zone centered on Clefable that persists for 3s. Inside the gravity zone, auto attacks change and deal increased damage. Enemies in the gravity zone have their movement speed decreased by 15% stacking up to 3 times gaining a stack whenever a set amount of time passes. These enemies are also unable to use Dash moves. If an enemy attempts to enter the gravity zone with a dash move, the dash move is stopped and that enemy is left unable to act for 1s.

98% SpA + 10 x (Level - 1) + 410

Widens this move’s area-of-effect and increases the duration of its effects to 4s.

Follow Me

7.50s Hindrance

Clefable moves to the designated location while waving its finger receiving a 3s shield. Attention of enemies hit and enemies near the designated location are drawn. These drawn enemies are forced to approach the user and attack Clefable with their auto attacks for 2s.

260% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 900

Increases Clefable's Defense by 150 for 3s and Sp. Def by 100 for 3s when this move is used.

Wonder Wish

Unite Move

89s 80000 Recovery

Unlocks at level 8

Clefable waggles their finger, restoring HP to allies in the area-of-effect. The lower an ally's HP is, the more HP this move restores to that ally. Afterward, Clefable gets a random move that can be performed by using the Unite Move again within 10s.

Note: Some random moves will activate immediately.

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 30% CDR, 20% Max HP Shield

Splash

Hops but nothing happens. Activates immediately and refunds 90% Unite Charge.

Explosion

Activates immediately, becoming unstoppable and dealing massive damage in an area at the cost of 40% of your maximum HP. This cost is unmitigable but will not KO you, instead leaving you at 1 HP.

486% SpA + 34 x (Level - 1) + 1640

Hydro Pump

Spits a powerful stream of water hitting three times and shoving targets back.

121.5% SpA + 9 x (Level - 1) + 410

Hyper Beam

Stands still and fires a targeted piercing beam dealing major damage. Firing rate is quick.

Against Wild Pokémon: The additional damage from max HP is capped at 2400.

243% SpA + 17 x (Level - 1) + 820

Block

Creates and holds a wall in a target direction, gaining a shield, becoming unstoppable and reducing all damage taken by 25% for 4s. Enemies that contact the wall are knocked back and stunned for 0.8s. Other abilities may not be activated during the block but existing moves may continue.

Close Combat

Launches a flurry of blows dealing damage and healing per target hit. Clefable is unstoppable during this move.

52.07% SpA + 4 x (Level - 1) + 176

10.4% SpA + 1 x (Level - 1) + 35

Fly

Leaps up into the air becoming untargetable, granted free movement, and increasing movement speed by 65% for 3s. After 3s or upon early activation, land in the area beneath dealing damage to enemies in the landing area.

315.9% SpA + 22 x (Level - 1) + 1066
